OL,3,C'Eid in the Park' prayers gathering
OL,4,Ccancelled over poor ground conditions
OL,6,FA large gathering to mark Eid-al-Fitr
OL,7,Fhas been postponed due to poor ground
OL,8,Fconditions.
OL,10,FOrganisers from Manchester City
OL,11,FCouncil and 'Eid in the Park' said wet
OL,12,Fweather had left Platt Fields Park, in
OL,13,FFallowfield, unable to accommodate the
OL,14,Fhundreds of vehicles needed to put on
OL,15,Fthe event.
OL,17,F'Eid in the Park' is usually attended
OL,18,Fby thousands of people, where Muslims
OL,19,Fcelebrate the end of Ramadan on Friday
OL,20,F20 March.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
