FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774015868
OL,3,C'Eid in the Park' prayers gathering
OL,4,Ccancelled over poor ground conditions
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Manchester has a strong network of
OL,8,Fmosques and community centres that
OL,9,Fhost multiple Eid prayer sessions
OL,10,Fevery year.
OL,12,F"In particular Alfurqan Masjid and
OL,13,FIslamic Centre, one of the largest
OL,14,Fmosques in the city, has confirmed
OL,15,Fthat it will host several Eid prayer
OL,16,Fsessions to help accommodate members
OL,17,Fof the community who would normally
OL,18,Fattend Eid in the Park.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774015868
OL,3,C'Eid in the Park' prayers gathering
OL,4,Ccancelled over poor ground conditions
OL,6,F"We encourage everyone to attend their
OL,7,Flocal mosques or neighbourhood prayer
OL,8,Farrangements, many of which will
OL,9,Forganise multiple sessions on Eid
OL,10,Fmorning to welcome worshippers safely
OL,11,Fand comfortably."
OL,13,FDespite the change to the organised
OL,14,Fprayers, the family funfair at Platt
OL,15,FFields Park is still due to go ahead
OL,16,Fas planned between 12.00pm and 6.00pm
OL,17,Fon Friday, Saturday and Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
