PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774015868
OL,3,C'Eid in the Park' prayers gathering
OL,4,Ccancelled over poor ground conditions
OL,6,FOrganisers say that Eid in the Park
OL,7,Fwill return later this year in May
OL,8,F2026, and this change is a 'one-off
OL,9,Fadjustment'.
OL,11,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,12,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,13,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,14,Four region.
